        <!-- Release notes (keep it brief) -->
        <releasenotes>
            <![CDATA[
            <h3>Version 2.0.53 - Fix Position Bar Tracking + Persist Progress Across Reloads</h3>

            <h4>Bug Fixes</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Position bar now tracks back-and-forth navigation (not stuck at furthest slide)</li>
                <li>Forward navigation from tag target slide now updates position correctly</li>
                <li>furthestSlide/grade no longer resets on page refresh after tag navigation</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>Changes</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Reverted suspend_data WRITE intercept to NO time limit (protects DB resume position)</li>
                <li>Track position from ORIGINAL suspend_data value (before write modification)</li>
                <li>Send actual slide number as directSlide to sendProgressUpdate</li>
                <li>Persist furthestSlide in sessionStorage to survive iframe reloads</li>
                <li>Applied same fixes to both SCORM 1.2 and SCORM 2004 handlers</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>Previous Version</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>v2.0.52: Added time limits to read intercepts (kept for reads, reverted for writes)</li>
            </ul>
